array = np.random.randint(1, 100, ARRAY_SIZE)
    mean = np.mean(array)
    std = np.std(array)

    # Create the histogram
    hist, _ = plt.hist(array, bins=100, color='C0', edgecolor='C0', alpha=0.65)
    plt.xlabel('Value')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
